        {
          "name": "Add Payment Card",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{ssoToken}}",
                "description": "JWT access token for authentication"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cardHolderName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"cardNumber\": \"4242424242424242\",\n  \"expiryMonth\": \"12\",\n  \"expiryYear\": \"2026\",\n  \"cvv\": \"123\",\n  \"cardType\": \"visa\",\n  \"billingAddress\": \"123 Main Street\",\n  \"billingCity\": \"New York\",\n  \"billingState\": \"NY\",\n  \"billingZipCode\": \"10001\",\n  \"billingCountry\": \"US\",\n  \"isDefault\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{paymentUrl}}/api/payment/wallet/cards",
              "host": ["{{paymentUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "payment", "wallet", "cards"]
            },
            "description": "Add a new payment card to the user's wallet\n\n**Body Parameters:**\n- `cardHolderName` (string, required): Name on the card\n- `cardNumber` (string, required): Card number\n- `expiryMonth` (string, required): Expiration month (MM)\n- `expiryYear` (string, required): Expiration year (YYYY)\n- `cvv` (string, required): CVV code\n- `cardType` (string, required): Card type (visa, mastercard, etc.)\n- `billingAddress` (string, optional): Billing street address\n- `billingCity` (string, optional): Billing city\n- `billingState` (string, optional): Billing state/province\n- `billingZipCode` (string, optional): Billing ZIP/postal code\n- `billingCountry` (string, optional): Billing country code (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2)\n- `isDefault` (boolean, optional): Set as default payment method"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get All Payment Cards",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
