              "path": ["api", "payment", "webhooks", "stripe"]
            },
            "description": "Handle Stripe webhook events\n\n**Headers:**\n- `Stripe-Signature` (string, required): Stripe signature for webhook verification\n\n**Body Parameters:**\n- `id` (string, required): Stripe event ID\n- `type` (string, required): Event type (payment_intent.succeeded, payment_intent.failed, etc.)\n- `data.object` (object, required): The payment intent or charge object"
