            "description": "Handle PayPal webhook events\n\n**Body Parameters:**\n- `id` (string, required): PayPal webhook ID\n- `event_type` (string, required): Event type (PAYMENT.CAPTURE.COMPLETED, etc.)\n- `resource` (object, required): The payment resource object"
